and a good job.

351
00:44:52.731 --> 00:44:54.358
Why would you
tell the other girls I am.

352
00:44:54.441 --> 00:44:57.653
and I quote.
"a fucking asshole"?

353
00:44:58.821 --> 00:45:00.155
I'm very grateful
for everything

354
00:45:00.239 --> 00:45:01.240
