but it's your lucky day.

364
00:46:17.357 --> 00:46:20.444
Ordinarily.
we'd slit your throat
in the name of our Lord.

365
00:46:20.527 --> 00:46:25.115
but one of our maids
was just caught stealing.

366
00:46:26.033 --> 00:46:28.160
