367
00:46:28.243 --> 00:46:32.289
Finally stop struggling
and have a home
where you belong.

368
00:46:32.372 --> 00:46:35.125
We'll take care of you.
Understand?

369
00:46:37.961 --> 00:46:39.338
Splendid.

370
00:46:50.974 --> 00:46:52.476
This is my home now.

371
00:46:55.729 --> 00:46:58.357
I'm not going
anywhere with you.

372
00:47:01.068 --> 00:47:03.779
